<reference id="enum_videomirrormodetype">
    <title><ph keyref="VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_TYPE"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">Video mirror mode.</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title>Enumerator</title>
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_AUTO"/></pt>
                <pd>0: The SDK determines the mirror mode.<ul>
                    <li>For the mirror mode of the local video view: If you use a front camera, the SDK enables the mirror mode by default; if you use a rear camera, the SDK disables the mirror mode by default.</li>
                    <li>For the remote user: The mirror mode is disabled by default.</li></ul></pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml>
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_ENABLED"/></pt>
                <pd>1: Enable mirror mode.</pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml>
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_DISABLED"/></pt>
                <pd>2: Disable mirror mode.</pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
